For this project :
Required Dependencies:
1. NodeJs
2. Docker
3. Java
4. Jenkins

A] For installation of these tools, scripts are used. The scripts are in the Scripts directory.

B] For containerization of the application, docker is used.
  i) Application and its dependencies are packaged into docker image, with the help of Dockerfile.
     Dockerfile is in the repository
  ii) The image is then run in container of docker 

C] To make this process fully automated, Jenkins is used as CI/CD tools
   i) One pipeline is created for CI and one for CD
   ii) The Jenkins pipeline is present in the repository.   
